text: Gibreel Ali (born 1924) is a Sudanese former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre rifle, three positions and 50 metre rifle, prone events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1924 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Sudanese male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Sudan Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics
